#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.151"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.151:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.151:0.2"
msgid "15. Navapurāṇavagga "
msgstr "15. The Old and the New "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 151. Antevāsikasutta → antevasi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.151:0.3"
msgid "151. Antevāsikasutta "
msgstr "151. A Student "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.151:1.1"
msgid "“Anantevāsikamidaṃ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ vussati anācariyakaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, this spiritual life is lived without a resident student and without a teaching master. "

#. VAR: phāsu → phāsuṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.151:1.2"
msgid "Santevāsiko, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sācariyako dukkhaṃ na phāsu viharati. "
msgstr "A mendicant who lives with a resident student and a teaching master lives in suffering and discomfort. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:1.3"
msgid "Anantevāsiko, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anācariyako sukhaṃ phāsu viharati. "
msgstr "A mendicant who lives without a resident student and a teaching master lives in happiness and comfort. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.151:1.4"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhu, santevāsiko sācariyako dukkhaṃ na phāsu viharati? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant who lives with a resident student and a teaching master live in suffering and discomfort? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.151:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā uppajjanti pāpakā akusalā dhammā sarasaṅkappā saṃyojaniyā. "
msgstr "When a mendicant sees a sight with the eye, bad, unskillful phenomena arise: memories and thoughts prone to fetters. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:1.6"
msgid "Tyāssa anto vasanti, antassa vasanti pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities reside within. Since they have bad unskillful qualities residing within, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:1.7"
msgid "Tasmā santevāsikoti vuccati. "
msgstr "they’re said to have a resident student. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:1.8"
msgid "Te naṃ samudācaranti, samudācaranti naṃ pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities master them. Since they’re mastered by bad unskillful qualities, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:1.9"
msgid "Tasmā sācariyakoti vuccati … pe …. "
msgstr "they’re said to have a teaching master. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.151:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā uppajjanti pāpakā akusalā dhammā sarasaṅkappā saṃyojaniyā. "
msgstr "Furthermore, when a mendicant hears … smells … tastes … touches … "

msgctxt "sn35.151:2.2"
msgid "Tyāssa anto vasanti, antassa vasanti pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.151:2.3"
msgid "Tasmā santevāsikoti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.151:2.4"
msgid "Te naṃ samudācaranti, samudācaranti naṃ pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. Tasmā sācariyakoti vuccati … pe …. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.137, sc3
msgctxt "sn35.151:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno manasā dhammaṃ viññāya uppajjanti pāpakā akusalā dhammā sarasaṅkappā saṃyojaniyā. "
msgstr "knows a thought with the mind, bad, unskillful phenomena arise: memories and thoughts prone to fetters. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:3.2"
msgid "Tyāssa anto vasanti, antassa vasanti pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities reside within. Since they have bad unskillful qualities residing within, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:3.3"
msgid "Tasmā santevāsikoti vuccati. "
msgstr "they’re said to have a resident student. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:3.4"
msgid "Te naṃ samudācaranti, samudācaranti naṃ pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities master them. Since they’re mastered by bad unskillful qualities, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:3.5"
msgid "Tasmā sācariyakoti vuccati. "
msgstr "they’re said to have a teaching master. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:3.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu santevāsiko sācariyako dukkhaṃ, na phāsu viharati. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant who lives with a resident student and a teaching master lives in suffering and discomfort. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn35.151:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anantevāsiko anācariyako sukhaṃ phāsu viharati? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant who lives without a resident student and a teaching master live in happiness and comfort? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.151:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā na uppajjanti pāpakā akusalā dhammā sarasaṅkappā saṃyojaniyā. "
msgstr "When a mendicant sees a sight with the eye, bad, unskillful phenomena don’t arise: memories and thoughts prone to fetters. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:4.3"
msgid "Tyāssa na anto vasanti, nāssa anto vasanti pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities don’t reside within. Since they don’t have bad unskillful qualities residing within, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:4.4"
msgid "Tasmā anantevāsikoti vuccati. "
msgstr "they’re said to not have a resident student. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:4.5"
msgid "Te naṃ na samudācaranti, na samudācaranti naṃ pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities don’t master them. Since they’re not mastered by bad unskillful qualities, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:4.6"
msgid "Tasmā anācariyakoti vuccati … pe …. "
msgstr "they’re said to not have a teaching master. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn35.151:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā na uppajjanti pāpakā akusalā dhammā sarasaṅkappā saṃyojaniyā. "
msgstr "Furthermore, when a mendicant hears … smells … tastes … touches … "

msgctxt "sn35.151:5.2"
msgid "Tyāssa na anto vasanti, nāssa anto vasanti pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.151:5.3"
msgid "Tasmā anantevāsikoti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.151:5.4"
msgid "Te naṃ na samudācaranti, na samudācaranti naṃ pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. Tasmā anācariyakoti vuccati … pe …. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.138, sc6
msgctxt "sn35.151:6.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno manasā dhammaṃ viññāya na uppajjanti pāpakā akusalā dhammā sarasaṅkappā saṃyojaniyā. "
msgstr "knows a thought with the mind, bad, unskillful phenomena don’t arise: memories and thoughts prone to fetters. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:6.2"
msgid "Tyāssa na anto vasanti, nāssa anto vasanti pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities don’t reside within. Since they don’t have bad unskillful qualities residing within, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:6.3"
msgid "Tasmā anantevāsikoti vuccati. "
msgstr "they’re said to not have a resident student. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:6.4"
msgid "Te naṃ na samudācaranti, na samudācaranti naṃ pāpakā akusalā dhammāti. "
msgstr "Those qualities don’t master them. Since they’re not mastered by bad unskillful qualities, "

msgctxt "sn35.151:6.5"
msgid "Tasmā anācariyakoti vuccati. "
msgstr "they’re said to not have a teaching master. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.151:6.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anantevāsiko anācariyako sukhaṃ phāsu viharati. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant who lives without a resident student and a teaching master lives in happiness and comfort. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.151:6.7"
msgid "Anantevāsikamidaṃ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "This spiritual life is lived without a resident student and without a teaching master. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:6.8"
msgid "Anācariyakaṃ santevāsiko, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sācariyako dukkhaṃ, na phāsu viharati. "
msgstr "A mendicant who lives with a resident student and a teaching master lives in suffering and discomfort. "

msgctxt "sn35.151:6.9"
msgid "Anantevāsiko, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anācariyako sukhaṃ phāsu viharatī”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant who lives without a resident student and a teaching master lives in happiness and comfort.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.151:6.10"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

